            </h3>
            <ul>
                <li class="mb-4">
                    <a class="inline-block text-coolGray-500 hover:text-coolGray-600 font-medium" href="/kiosk-betreiber/andy-grunwald/">
                        <span class="inline-block text-coolGray-500 hover:text-coolGray-600 font-medium">
                            Andy Grunwald
                        </span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li class="mb-4">
                    <a class="inline-block text-coolGray-500 hover:text-coolGray-600 font-medium" href="/kiosk-betreiber/wolfgang-gassler/">
